## 🔗 有用命令

### 状态检查

```bash
# 深度状态
openclaw status --deep

# 渠道状态
openclaw status --deep | grep -E "(Channel|ON|OK)"

# 服务状态
systemctl --user status {{ openclaw_systemd_service }}

# 日志
journalctl --user -u {{ openclaw_systemd_service }} -f
```

### 密钥管理

```bash
# 审计密钥
openclaw secrets audit

# 重新加载密钥
openclaw secrets reload

# 检查密钥文件权限
ls -la {{ openclaw_config_dir }}/runtime-secrets.json {{ openclaw_config_dir }}/gateway.env
```

### 服务管理

```bash
# 重启服务
systemctl --user restart {{ openclaw_systemd_service }}

# 停止服务
systemctl --user stop {{ openclaw_systemd_service }}

# 启用开机启动
systemctl --user enable {{ openclaw_systemd_service }}
```

